    "In Turing's terms, LLMs are essentially machines performing verbal behavior and that do not know what they are saying.",
    "They computationally generate a right word sequence by computing the probability of sequences of token.",
    "In essence, they predict language and do not produce language.",
    "This underscores their generative capability; while impressive, it is a good performance, not intelligence.",
    "So, what precisely are they?"
  ],
